  "detailed_description": "<strong>Pure Rock Crawling</strong> is a physics based off-road simulator. Developed by one developer. <br>Immerse yourself in the world of rock crawling as you drive capable off-road trucks. Featuring soft body tires physics, complex drivetrain simulation, maps made with photogrammetry, visual and mechanical customization.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824720/extras/c3d83a3de589439ef904864b7862e29b.poster.avif?t=1743516151\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824720/extras/c3d83a3de589439ef904864b7862e29b.webm?t=1743516151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824720/extras/c3d83a3de589439ef904864b7862e29b.mp4?t=1743516151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Suspension customization - equip a variety of addons that affect your riding characteristics. Different suspension types, flexible tires and lift kits. All physics based providing true to life suspension articulation and tire deformation.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824720/extras/17af0d23093f22e17514bfad0785bb7a.poster.avif?t=1743516151\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824720/extras/17af0d23093f22e17514bfad0785bb7a.webm?t=1743516151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824720/extras/17af0d23093f22e17514bfad0785bb7a.mp4?t=1743516151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Visual customization - choose between many bumpers, doors, roof addons, fenders, vinyl wraps and decals. Make your ride your own and hit the trails with style.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824720/extras/2ba15752078b12024478839d351a0ff9.poster.avif?t=1743516151\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824720/extras/2ba15752078b12024478839d351a0ff9.webm?t=1743516151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824720/extras/2ba15752078b12024478839d351a0ff9.mp4?t=1743516151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Challenge yourself on marked trails or just roam around. Pure Rock Crawling is a free roam game that offers additional challenges in the form of completing the trails. Main focus is to provide you a playground for best rock crawling experience in a physics based simulation of suspension and tires.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824720/extras/2572c281a3df16c5c005429e73866481.poster.avif?t=1743516151\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824720/extras/2572c281a3df16c5c005429e73866481.webm?t=1743516151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824720/extras/2572c281a3df16c5c005429e73866481.mp4?t=1743516151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore variety of maps, take on challenges and have fun rock crawling !<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824720/extras/69a393b4c57386c70318115b403e2fd9.poster.avif?t=1743516151\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824720/extras/69a393b4c57386c70318115b403e2fd9.webm?t=1743516151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824720/extras/69a393b4c57386c70318115b403e2fd9.mp4?t=1743516151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Pure Rock Crawling</strong> is a physics based off-road simulator. Developed by one developer. <br>Immerse yourself in the world of rock crawling as you drive capable off-road trucks. Featuring soft body tires physics, complex drivetrain simulation, maps made with photogrammetry, visual and mechanical customization.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824720/extras/c3d83a3de589439ef904864b7862e29b.poster.avif?t=1743516151\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824720/extras/c3d83a3de589439ef904864b7862e29b.webm?t=1743516151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824720/extras/c3d83a3de589439ef904864b7862e29b.mp4?t=1743516151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Suspension customization - equip a variety of addons that affect your riding characteristics. Different suspension types, flexible tires and lift kits. All physics based providing true to life suspension articulation and tire deformation.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824720/extras/17af0d23093f22e17514bfad0785bb7a.poster.avif?t=1743516151\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824720/extras/17af0d23093f22e17514bfad0785bb7a.webm?t=1743516151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824720/extras/17af0d23093f22e17514bfad0785bb7a.mp4?t=1743516151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Visual customization - choose between many bumpers, doors, roof addons, fenders, vinyl wraps and decals. Make your ride your own and hit the trails with style.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824720/extras/2ba15752078b12024478839d351a0ff9.poster.avif?t=1743516151\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824720/extras/2ba15752078b12024478839d351a0ff9.webm?t=1743516151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824720/extras/2ba15752078b12024478839d351a0ff9.mp4?t=1743516151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Challenge yourself on marked trails or just roam around. Pure Rock Crawling is a free roam game that offers additional challenges in the form of completing the trails. Main focus is to provide you a playground for best rock crawling experience in a physics based simulation of suspension and tires.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824720/extras/2572c281a3df16c5c005429e73866481.poster.avif?t=1743516151\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824720/extras/2572c281a3df16c5c005429e73866481.webm?t=1743516151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824720/extras/2572c281a3df16c5c005429e73866481.mp4?t=1743516151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore variety of maps, take on challenges and have fun rock crawling !<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824720/extras/69a393b4c57386c70318115b403e2fd9.poster.avif?t=1743516151\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824720/extras/69a393b4c57386c70318115b403e2fd9.webm?t=1743516151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824720/extras/69a393b4c57386c70318115b403e2fd9.mp4?t=1743516151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
